name: Hexpo
description: Curate your own Hic et Nunc gallery! Hexpo is a gallery tool for hic et nunc, created as a result of the first Hicathon. This is the logo of the project, a collaborative generative piece that takes its final shape based on how many editions of the OBJKT are collected within 48 hours after its creation. Visit hexpo.andreasrau.eu to see the logo in context, and curate your own gallery.
